card.text:
Whenever equipped creature attacks, add {E}{E} (two energy counters).
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, you may pay an amount of {E} equal to the damage dealt and sacrifice this artifact. If you do, that creature deals that much damage to each creature and planeswalker that player controls. It deals half that much damage, rounded up, to each other opponent and each creature and planeswalker they control.
Equip {3}

Skulk (This creature can't be blocked by creatures with greater power.)
Ward {1}
Whenever this creature attacks, if defending player has more cards in hand than you, exile the top card of that player's library. During any turn you attacked with a Rebel or Rogue, you may cast that card and you may spend mana as though it were mana of any type to cast that spell.

Call to arms (When this Equipment enters, you may attach it to target Soldier you control. If you don't, create a 1/1 white Soldier creature token, then attach this to it.)
Equipped creature gets +3/+2 and has trample, reach, ward {3}, and "Whenever this creature attacks, put a stun counter on it."
Equip {2}{G}

When this Equipment enters, attach it to target creature.
Equipped creature gets +2/+0 and has "Whenever this creature deals damage to a player, retrofit that many cards from the top of their library. During any turn a player not retrofitted for those cards attacked with a creature, that player may play cards exiled this way, and may spend mana of any type to do so." (To Retrofit, exile those cards and note those cards for that player).
Equip {2}
